data.description: Your vision! Your home! Envision this large beautifully maintained home yours. Displaying hardwood floors, 5+ Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms, great decor, modern kitchen with granite counters, and stainless steel appliances. Upstairs features 2 bedrooms with skylights and a separate den area. Full-finish basement with an additional bedroom. The private yard is great for entertaining, and the 2 car garage often doubles as additional entertainment space. Nothing to do but move in. Tree-lined street with neighbors who show pride in ownership. Seller motivated. Schedule your tour today.
